The '''Bagå Formation''' is a [[geological formation]] dating to around 199 to 170 million years ago, in the Early and Late Jurassic. It is located on the island of [[Bornholm]], [[Denmark]].<ref name=bonde>Bonde, N. (2012). "Danish Dinosaurs: A Review". In Godefroit, P. ''Bernissart Dinosaurs''. Indiana University Press. pp. 435-449.</ref>
