==Date==

Monday is the first day of the week.

==Time==
The [[24-hour clock|24-hour notation]] almost exclusively, with a colon as the standardised and recommended separator (e.g. 18:56). In spoken or informal Ukrainian, [[12-hour|12-hour notation]] can be used, but in this case in general no am/pm specification used, so this information is expected to be gained from context. Another difference from English is that half-hours are counted up to next hour: {{lang|uk|"половина восьмої"}}, literally  “half of eight” means 7:30, not 8:30.

