{{Italic title}} {{Taxobox | name = Purple swift | image = | image_width = 204px | image_caption = | regnum = [[Animal]]ia | phylum = [[Arthropod]]a | classis = [[Insect]]a | ordo = [[Lepidoptera]] | familia = [[Hesperiidae]] | genus = ''[[Mimene]]'' | species = '''''M. atropatene''''' | binomial = ''Mimene atropatene'' | binomial_authority = ([[Hans Fruhstorfer|Fruhstorfer]], 1911) | synonyms = *''Parnara atropatene'' <small>Fruhstorfer, 1911</small> *''Telesto wollastoni'' <small>Rothschild, 1915</small> }}
'''''Mimene atropatene''''', the '''purple swift''', is a [[butterfly]] of the family [[Hesperiidae]]. It is found along the north-eastern coast of [[Queensland]], as well as on the [[Aru Islands]], [[Irian Jaya]] and [[Papua New Guinea]].
The [[wingspan]] is about 40&nbsp;mm.
