The '''İzmir Kentkart''' is a proximity type [[smart card]] used for payment in public transport of [[İzmir]], [[Turkey]]. The card was launched on March 15, 1999 and has monthly collector cards.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.izmirdebugun.com/root.vol?exec=page&nid=7523 |newspaper=İzmir'de Bugün.com |title=Kentkart |date=2010-09-08 |language=Turkish |accessdate=2011-02-13 }}</ref> The İzmir Kentkart is a part of the [[Kentkart]] project in Turkey launched in 1998.<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.kentkart.com/Tarihce.aspx |publisher=Kentkart |title=Tarihçe |language=Turkish |accessdate=2011-02-13 }}</ref>
